data.description: 3/2 with AMAZING BONUS ROOM, formal living, formal dining, Kitchen open to living and dining, and spacious rooms!  This charming home built in 1945 has unique features that will set it apart.  The large bonus room features a massive walk-in closet and separate door to exterior that could be used as home office, game room, bedroom, etc.  Builtins that are original create a sense of history and nostalgia.  This home was renovated in 2012 and since then the Sellers have done even more to make this house truly a home you could brag on.  Lovely courtyard in the back provides privacy and a nice size side yard offers space for playing.  No joking, you really have to see this home to appreciate the space and what it has to offer to you and your family.  Make an appointment today!
